title: We welcome you and your fur babies to your new home!
posting_body: ['16100 Linden Ave N, Shoreline, WA 98133', 'Located in Shoreline, Washington youll find comfort and convenience in this spacious, luxury apartment community.', 'Junction160 is nearby many shops, restaurants, major bus stops and the interurban trail.', 'The community was recently renovated and many of the amenities and homes are like-new.', 'Residents enjoy spending time in the movie room and entertaining in the recreation room.', 'Bike storage is also available to all residents, and the community offers ample parking.', 'Schedule a tour today to see why residents love calling Junction 160 home.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Washer and Dryer', 'In Each Home', 'Balcony', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Brand New Hardwood Floors', 'Community Features:', 'Ample Parking', 'Translation Service Available', 'Movie Room', 'Recreation Room', 'Bike Storage', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
